Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:31.05,ShowTitle,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Interviews with Monster Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:52.96,BlackWhite,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Shibasaki High School \N{\c&H8074D7&}Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:52.96,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd be able to hide that \NI'm a snow woman in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:56.98,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,If word didn't get around that I was a demi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:02:00.63,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,maybe no one would approach \Nme out of curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:02.43,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,If I kept my distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe my nature wouldn't cause \Nproblems for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:08.69,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:14.11,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,When I got overheated during PE class,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:12.80,Default - flashback,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kusakabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.11,Default - flashback,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You okay, Kusakabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:16.49,Default - flashback,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Do you feel sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:17.38,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,someone was about to touch me, \Nso without thinking, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.60,Default - flashback,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a snow woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:20.49,Default - flashback,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:23.78,Default - flashback,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay once I cool down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:27.50,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,But I ended up fainting and being \Ncarried out on a stretcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.16,Default - flashback,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Stretcher! Someone get a stretcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:33.71,Title1,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(487,1)}Snow Woman-chan Is Cold
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:37.01,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Have you hidden the fact that you're \Na snow woman all your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:39.64,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, not before I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.83,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Until I started high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lived in a rural town, with lots of snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:47.53,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I didn't hide it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.47,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,When my temperature got low,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:53.73,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I occasionally emanated cold air or \Nmy tears became ice, but that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.33,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,No one else was affected,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I considered it a minor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:03.16,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,So I never had any problems with \Nmy nature as a snow woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:08.33,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Then, something happened between \Nmoving here and starting high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.93,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:14.21,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It was right after I moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:17.50,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I was really depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:22.24,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried about how I'd \Nfit into a new environment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:25.85,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,And I was separated from the friends \NI'd known since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.38,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd always lived in the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:31.81,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,so I wasn't sure if I could make it in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.01,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:39.00,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I wished I could dissolve into the \Nhot water, like in a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.47,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought about all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something suddenly felt strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.70,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Ice formed in your hot bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.92,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It spooked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:52.26,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The ice melted quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:56.17,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,but if I'd put out enough cold \Nair to freeze hot water...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.92,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The idea was absolutely terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:03.88,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,If I directed that cold air at\Nsomeone, what would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:08.55,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,When my high school life began, \NI was still stressed about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:11.56,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I avoided contact with \Neveryone, I thought I'd be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.48,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you started \Nsteering clear of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.87,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:19.01,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how dangerous I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:21.82,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew that, and could convey it to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:25.36,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I could proudly tell everyone \Nthat I'm a snow woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.37,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Cold air freezing hot water...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:31.93,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,How do you normally take baths?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:32.68,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.85,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I mean, what's the water temperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you take them with family members?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.62,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The same way as everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:41.94,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,About 40 degrees Celsius...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:45.72,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,But people say I take relatively short baths.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:48.26,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,And what was that bath like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.85,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Was the water any cooler than usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.18,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:55.05,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:57.45,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You said your tears also turn to ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.32,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't crying or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:03.38,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The piece of ice just floated \Nup, all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:04.49,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.89,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What about sweat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the bath made you \Nsweat, and that froze?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:11.89,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I almost never sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:15.71,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It might be more accurate \Nto say that I can't sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.00,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.71,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,My... sweat glands?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:23.64,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Right, the glands that secrete sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.67,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Evidently, I have very few of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:27.01,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:30.67,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't as if I don't sweat at all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:33.23,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Then, is it possible your sweat froze?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:36.52,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,My sweat hasn't ever frozen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:39.97,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It seems strange it would \Nonly freeze this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:41.61,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:46.74,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,My tears can freeze anytime, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:51.33,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to spend the whole lunch \Nperiod talking about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:54.42,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.53,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:05:59.96,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You can go back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.91,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:03.62,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kusakabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:04.17,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:06.86,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,If you're okay with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.30,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,would you come see me after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.22,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.07,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.86,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi-san! Machi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.14,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have lunch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.00,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.53,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, you should join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:26.93,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Talking with Takahashi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About something specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:33.22,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I think I said some weird \Nthings and worried him even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:35.12,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, don't worry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:39.07,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei always wants to talk \Nto demi-chans, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.09,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:41.71,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:45.84,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Want to get some \Nice cream after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:46.97,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.18,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.58,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I found a great place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.62,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:52.51,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.18,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.62,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.35,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,The cold air her body generated
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:01.85,BlackWhite,Text,0000,0000,0000,,snow woman
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.73,BlackWhite,Text,0000,0000,0000,,snow woman \N\Nsnow woman stories \Nsnow woman soft
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:05.61,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,created ice, without lowering \Nthe water temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:03.81,BlackWhite,Text,0000,0000,0000,,snow woman
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:04.86,BlackWhite,Text,0000,0000,0000,,snow woman
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:05.61,BlackWhite,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}snow woman — Wukupedia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.57,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:12.11,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,And her tears freeze anytime...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.57,SignB,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Antiques and Ghost Stories
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.57,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:16.40,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll check folklore first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.12,SignB,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}Koizumi Yakumo              {\fs16}Antiques and Ghost Stories
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:32.92,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oddly enough, all the legends about \Nsnow women are kind of sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:38.27,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I did some more research on snow women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:42.10,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Their appearance is basically \Nthe same in every legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:46.70,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful women, dressed all \Nin white, with long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.82,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Some describe elderly women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.02,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,All share a basic template.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:55.39,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,The snow woman approaches a man, \Nnot telling him that she's a snow woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.12,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,and she asks him for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.63,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,If he refuses, she does something mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:03.90,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Or if he befriends her, an accident \Noccurs, and she disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.83,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Some minor details vary by region,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.71,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,but they're all basically one or the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.67,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:14.50,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.14,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:18.26,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Do your feet get cold when you're nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.69,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yes, actually, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.39,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I get cold easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:24.35,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.19,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:37.33,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to tell Kusakabe something \Nthat might really hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:40.99,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But I want her to overcome it. \NIf she can, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:43.96,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.18,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I mean, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:49.04,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,There, we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.68,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is that hot water?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:52.80,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a foot bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:53.65,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.37,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.98,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,How's the temperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.15,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:06.90,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.98,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Would you read this aloud for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:12.32,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I compiled some legends \Nabout snow women.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.90,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is this necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.15,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:20.23,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,As much as it pains me, I want you \Nto read it and memorize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.83,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:25.88,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,"One night, amidst a raging blizzard, \Na beautiful woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:29.75,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,with long hair and white clothes, \Ncame to a certain man's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:33.21,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Her body was as cold as ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:36.66,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,So he tried to get her to bathe,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.89,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,but she vehemently refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:41.44,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,He forced her into the bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she dissolved into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.81,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Only a shard of ice remained."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.52,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:50.72,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:55.06,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,"Two woodcutters lived in a certain village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:56.82,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,One winter night,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they were inside, sheltering from the cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:04.88,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,when a woman clad in white, \Nwith cold eyes, appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.96,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The woman breathed her white \Nbreath upon the older man,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:14.46,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,and he was instantly encased in ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:20.42,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The younger man was so shocked, \Nhe could do nothing but watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:25.34,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The woman hovered over the younger man,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:29.60,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,but she only smiled at him \Nand didn't take his life..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:33.03,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Kusaka—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.31,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:34.99,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.07,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.61,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-Ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:41.74,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:43.95,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:45.00,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:45.66,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You were?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:48.25,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,See? This ice is your sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:51.24,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sweat? But I don't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:53.78,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,This is the sweat produced \Ndue to emotional stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.30,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What they call a "cold sweat."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:57.19,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,A cold sweat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:00.81,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when I asked if your feet \Nget cold when you're nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:01.26,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:05.93,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Cold sweat usually breaks out on \Nyour forehead, palms, and soles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:06.85,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:10.35,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You sweat from \Nthe soles of your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:11.96,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you figure that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:14.82,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the legends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.78,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Most snow woman legends are sad stories
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:22.41,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,about unfulfilled love, isolation, \Nand melting away into dew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.49,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:27.71,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,that negative feelings and emotional stress
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:31.04,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,must play a major role in \Na snow woman's nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:34.67,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Then, sweat due to stress would \Nprobably freeze, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:37.76,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to put all that strain on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:38.30,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:43.60,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prove my theory, I had to \Nmake you as nervous as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:44.51,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:45.73,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you did it to assuage my concerns!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.85,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,This does assuage them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:51.99,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ice in the bath was your cold sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:58.44,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It happened because you were thinking \Nabout things that made you tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:02.20,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning, you don't need to worry \Nabout the cold air you generate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:05.66,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It's barely enough to cool hot water at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:09.19,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,A snow woman's peculiarities are minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:12.80,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,The way you felt about your nature \Nin middle school wasn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:16.88,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry or stress \Nyourself about, Kusakabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:20.76,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't the kind of demi \Nthat would hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.30,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.97,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:29.14,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:33.83,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,If a snow woman's unique traits occur \Nas a result of negative emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:36.73,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,then they won't occur if \Nshe's happy and relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:39.32,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Warm tears don't freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:43.46,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I hope you'll be able \Nto shed lots of those tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:49.99,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What words would you use to describe \Nmy nature as a snow woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.26,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The crystallization of bodily fluids \Nreleased under stress," perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.52,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You're literally a "crystallization \Nof sweat and tears"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:06.77,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm sorry I didn't know \Nhow to react to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.47,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.59,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what are you going to \Ndo with that frozen sweat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:15.15,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:18.56,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Since I have it, I thought I'd analyze \Nits components at my college—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.88,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Analyze its components?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:20.85,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no less than sexual harassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:23.65,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.69,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.78,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.89,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:31.62,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I'm a snow woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.13,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see Yukki in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:37.47,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she already went home...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.08,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi-san! Machi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.17,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yukki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:43.59,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:46.48,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in such a rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:48.09,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.93,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:55.93,ShowTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,Interviews with Monster Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:57.81,Default,Vendor,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your mango ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.01,Default,Vendor,0000,0000,0000,,Come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:00.94,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.04,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The ice cream's really good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.66,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I-It sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.20,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:17.76,Default - italics,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met Yukki, I clung to her a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.81,Default - italics,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But she didn't seem to like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:21.78,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so I put a little distance between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.86,Default - italics,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And then, that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:25.26,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes, Yukki is a demi, but it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.72,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Macchi? Is it hard for you to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.18,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,It's in a cup, so I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.80,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:31.55,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.48,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:36.70,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,W-Would you like... a taste of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.40,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.71,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:42.86,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yay—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:49.04,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'd love some...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.78,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.65,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The mint is so refreshing and tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:54.69,Default - italics,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy Yukki invited me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:55.62,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I-Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.70,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but I wonder how she feels about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.06,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:03.30,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Sorry, Yukki! I ate too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.67,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.14,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:17.49,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, there's something I want \Nto apologize to you for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:22.74,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You realized that I avoided contact \Nwith others, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:27.48,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,So you stopped clinging to me, \Nlike you did when we first met,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.31,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,and started to keep a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:32.95,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I was really happy that \Nyou were so considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:37.37,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,But if you felt bad because of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:39.63,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.03,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't feel bad at al—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:44.11,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:44.50,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:49.40,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to interacting \Nwith people, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:51.63,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I've reached a compromise \Nwith myself, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:53.30,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:56.94,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,from now on, you can touch me all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:59.18,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can even cling to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:02.52,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yukki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.23,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, that didn't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:07.37,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:10.80,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd made you hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.53,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:18.43,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But I was so happy when you \Ninvited me to come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.09,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:22.46,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yukki, but can I bite you a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.15,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:24.41,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You'll suck my blood—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:25.79,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:30.26,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, my teeth sort of itch sometimes, \Nand I want to chew on someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.24,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Chew on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.67,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Just a tiny bit, through your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.04,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:35.59,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.05,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here I come—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:44.95,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Nom, nom, nom, nom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:41.06,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that tickles...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:45.69,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, T-Takanashi-san... \NW-Wait, time-out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.00,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Machi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:50.48,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,I've, also,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:54.68,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,wanted to be friends with you \Nfor a long time, Kusakabe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.58,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.57,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Machi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:58.97,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.32,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nom, nom, nom, nom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:02.22,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you're doing this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:05.46,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands feel so nice and cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:07.48,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Machi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:13.09,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Back when there was still \Nsegregation and opposition,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:17.55,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,legends about demis were born of \Nemotions such as awe and fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:21.56,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there aren't many happy, \Nlight-hearted legends about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:24.42,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Snow women, with their particular traits,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.56,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,often met tragic endings in their stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:30.66,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't believe snow women today
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:34.43,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,are fated to walk the path of \Ntheir counterparts in legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.32,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Because at the very least...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:42.10,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:45.59,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,...this snow woman is friends with \Na vampire and a dullahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:48.91,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,There are no legends about a \Ngroup like that anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:53.28,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,When you want to bite people, \Nwhat do you normally do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.33,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I ask Himari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:58.46,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Himari... Nom, nom, nom, nom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.53,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nom, nom, nom, nom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:02.15,Default - flashback,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the page.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:04.35,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nom, nom, nom, nom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:07.83,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Himari-san must be really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.16,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:08.91,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:10.94,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Eating lunch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:12.43,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:13.62,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:15.82,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to see you're all such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:19.86,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Hikari and Kyouko have \Nbeen wonderful to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:21.91,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari? Kyouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:25.08,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's nothing wrong with me \Ncalling them by name, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.44,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you're so close,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:30.23,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,but just try not to get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:32.34,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe and Machi should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:35.61,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But, Hikari, you'd better be a little careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.31,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what do you mean? No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:40.72,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you only use Hikari's given name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.97,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, because of Himari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:46.83,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:49.30,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You used "chan" for Himari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.82,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Good morning, Takanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:56.43,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:57.24,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.32,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.51,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:00.99,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That reaction seems annoying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.12,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.78,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.79,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, I kind of get the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:10.14,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Then, couldn't you use Kyouko's \Ngiven name, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.75,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't mind that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:14.88,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.88,Default - italics,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouko. Kyouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.47,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you can just call me "Machi."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.42,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:24.58,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! She shot you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.85,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey! Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:26.85,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:28.96,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:29.40,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:31.79,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's a little embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.77,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:35.23,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, my family name, Machi, \Nsounds a bit like a given name,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.86,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm happy to be called that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.48,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,For starters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:43.99,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to talk about others \Nwith given names, start with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:43.51,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Aw, he caught me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:47.08,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,"Yukki" and "Macchi" are one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.45,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.72,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What about Katou-sensei, \Nthe Japanese teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:52.14,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Katou-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:53.81,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,And Yachigusa-sensei, the school nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:54.92,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yachigusa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:58.37,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,See? You address all the others properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:19:59.92,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,so why call only me "Sensei"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.50,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just call me "Takahashi-sensei"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:06.04,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But you just seem like a "Sensei."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.12,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:07.70,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.97,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I totally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:12.48,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what do you call Satou-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:13.52,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sakki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.39,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Sakki? Is she your friend now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:20.28,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Was Kusakabe always that cheerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.36,Default,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.78,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hikari-chan. Fifth period is P.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.16,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! We have to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.46,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:27.95,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:28.49,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.82,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.75,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,She's so boisterous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.31,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.96,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll get going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.60,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:39.60,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.59,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.31,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:44.66,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Then, see you later,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:45.55,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:50.47,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Er, I thought maybe you wanted \Nme to call you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.81,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:56.33,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it doesn't matter what you call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:57.56,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:00.47,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I wasn't even thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:02.92,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,After Sensei barged in, I completely forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:04.10,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:05.48,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takanashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:07.53,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? We're kinda in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:09.28,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a nickname, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:12.81,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm not really sure I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.56,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:17.15,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Anything is fine, so just give me one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.34,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. What was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.96,Default,Ohta,0000,0000,0000,,You're in different classes. It happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:27.81,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Satake-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:34.08,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, when I collapsed before, \Nthanks for asking if I was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:36.02,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it took me so long to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:41.27,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Also, sorry for being mean after you were \Nkind enough to invite me to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.78,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,So, would you like to hang \Nout today, after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:45.94,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we could go for karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:47.91,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.66,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Great! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:56.96,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:01.00,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're the only boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.20,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Satake-kun, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,Title2,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time \NThe Takanashi Sisters Are Undeniable
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:38.13,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next time on {\i1}Interviews with Monster Girls:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.13,0:23:39.95,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The Takanashi Sisters Don't Fight.
